1988 BMW 7 Series · Sedan · Driven 109,000 miles

Last call for parts before the crusher gets it on 5/23!!!

1988 750iL 
- lots of parts already removed
- let me know what you need off the shell and comment for any other parts you want
- taking best offer on all parts, I want to help people out rather than make a profit
- willing to cut any sheetmetal off the body for anyone since the body is very straight on this one

Parts already pulled:

- full black power heated interior - front and rear seats, door panels (no shades), dash, glovebox, left hand drive knee pad, both center consoles w/factory car phone mount
- factory cat-back exhaust, muffler and resonator are stamped BMW and in amazing shape
- manual rear sunshade that works perfectly (parcel shelf is damaged but shade is perfect)
- headlights, one has a cracked lens
- taillights in perfect condition
- front and rear bumpers with all chrome trim in great shape with no damage, need paint
- headlight washer pumps
- engine has 109k
- MAF's

Many more! See less
